what

Worst: {{champion:163}} 

Not necessarily bad, but it's really unsatisfying having to make sure you're near the wall at all times to use it when you could be looking mid, bot, top, or anywhere that isn't your character walking back to lane, making a roam, or perusing the map mid/late-game. 

Best: {{champion:28}} 

Probably not the best of any champion but of the ones I play she's definitely at the top. The health regen is extremely useful with a ton of AP and is pretty much a free warmogs passive once you get a Deathcap. Invisibility is also very vital to her kit and makes her really fun to use, especially when you take advantage of the blocked sightlines from dead towers and bushes.
